    <summary>Bambu Suite is Bambu Lab’s desktop application for laser engraving, blade cutting, and pen drawing, providing a unified workspace for layout, toolpath preparation, preview, and job management.</summary>
    <description>Bambu Suite is a desktop application for integrating non-printing workflows with compatible Bambu hardware.

### Features
- Unified workspace for laser engraving, blade cutting, and pen drawing
- Toolpath preparation with preview and optimizations
- Project and job management for supported devices

### What this package does
- Installs Bambu Suite for Windows via the official installer
- Suitable for unattended/automated deployments with Chocolatey

### Compatibility and requirements
- Windows 10/11 (per upstream support)
- Administrator privileges may be required

### Verification after installation
- Launch “Bambu Suite”, create a sample project, and run a preview to verify the toolchain

